  ('fire-eq-tech-moex-02225', 'fire-eq-tech', 'fire-eq-tech-moex-102-5f3f518e', 'sub-fire-eq-tech-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關二氧化碳（CO）滅火劑之敘述，何者有誤？ 2', '["二氧化碳（CO）滅火劑滅火後不留痕跡 2", "二氧化碳（CO）滅火作用較氮氣（N）為大", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:11:23+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "029117514a32", "answer_pdf_sha1": "8ffbcb41409b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102070", "c": "902", "s": "0707", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "火災學概要", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年專技驗船師引水人、第一次食品技師考試消防設備人員地政士專責報關人員保險人員考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "fire-equipment-technician", "db_exam_id": "fire-eq-tech"}'::jsonb, NULL),
